title: AHS | Pumped up kicks (Murder House)
author: Noemi Mtz
comment: lol I was the kid in highschool who on a bad day came in with my hair slicked back, trench coat and black lipstick and eyes blackened to look like eye holes on a skull lol. I was fucking tate

My favorite thing about Murder House was that Tate was the real monster. While his all siblings had something off about them PHYSICALLY, all his problems were on the inside. I just loved it...how Constance was like, "AT LAST. A NORMAL CHILD" and he shoots up a school. It's not a new trope, but I thought it was a clever take on 'don't judge a book by its cover'. He was such a good villain.
He was for sure the most interesting character on this season
"When the quiet kid comes to school with a guitar case, but he plays the piano"
